    "body": "Glad it worked for you. I have always had the equal sign there and Docker's own documentation shows using the equal sign. Not sure why it doesn't work for you. You may want to get Docker to fix their docs at the very least.\r\n\r\nFrom https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/run/\r\n\r\n> Use the following command to run htop inside a container:\r\n> \r\n> $ docker run -it --rm --pid=host myhtop",
